snippet.title: Zombo Buster Rising Official Trailer 2014
snippet.description: Zombo Buster has finished their mission a while ago with the elevator technique. Meanwhile, some hopeless survivors are still struggling against horde of zombies. Screw the strategy, it's time to shoot'em all!
